      "text": "Teizeet to KUNGU win- \ntu/ ka ar Apgehrbu / Uhd\nna Engeti/ juhs stipri Karrotaji/\nstabweja pahr teem Kalneem.\nkas winna Wahrdü padarra /\npaklausidaimi winna Wahrdü tee behdse/ un no tawa Peh\nBaltim."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Teizeet to KUNGU wiſti\ntu/ ka ar Apgehrbu / Uhd\nwinna spehzigt Bulki/ juhs win-\ntahs Eeleijas grimme us to W\nna Sullaini/ kas pehz winna tu/ ko tu teem bij lizzis.\nPrahtu darra."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Teizeet to KUNGU wiſti tahs tee ne pahrkahpj / un\ntu/ ka ar Apgehrbu / Uhd\nwinna Darbi/ wiſtâs Weetâs/\nSeimmi wairs ne apkahs.\nkur wiꞥſch walda. Teiz to KUN-\nGU manna Dwehfele."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta ClV. Dseefma.\nWeena Pateikfchanas-Dseefma par to brihni,\ngu Raddifchanu un Waldifchanu wiſtas\nka Swehrus/ tur atdserrahs t\nPafaules/ un wiſtu radditu Leetu : 1/ etc.\nMescha-Ehseti.\nPar ko mum8 Deewu buhs flaweht un pa,\nteikt : 33."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eiz to KUNGU manna\nappakfch Debbefim / un dsee\nDwehfele / KUNG S\nstarp teem Sarreem.\nmans Deews / tu eſfi\nfohti leels/ ar Augftibu un Goh-\ndibu aptehrpees."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Gaischtba irr tas Ap-\ngehrbs/ ar ko tu apfedsees/ tu is-\nplatti to Debbeti/ ka weenu Gar-\ndint."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu leež tahs Augftibus\nGrihdi ar Uhdeni/ tu darri tahs\nPadebbejis par taweem Rat-\nteem/ tu dsennees us ta Wehja\nSpahrneem."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu darri tawus Eegetus\npar Barreem/ un tawus Sul-\ninus par Ugguns Leesmahm.\nTu (ent) kas to Seumi"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tohs Dsittmus ap-\nka ta muhscham ne kad kust\n6. Tohs Dsittmus ap-\ntu/ ka ar Apgehrbu / Uhd\nstabweja pahr teem Kalneem."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No tawas Lammascha-\nna tee steidsahs nohst."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee Kalnt angstejahs/\ntahs Eeleijas grimme us to W"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu eſti teem Eschas lizz"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu iswaddi Awosch-\neekfch Eeleijahn/ ka tee starp tee\nKalneem tekt."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee dsirdina wiſns La-\nka Swehrus/ tur atdserrahs t\nMescha-Ehseti."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pee teem miht tee Put-\nappakfch Debbefim / un dsee\nstarp teem Sarreem."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu flappini tohs Kalnu\nno augſchenes/ no teem Aug-\nteem/ ko tu darri/ tohp ta Seim\nnie peepildita."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu leež Sahli aug-\npreeksch Lohpeem/ un Sattumi\nZilwekam par labbu / tu iswed-\nMaisi no Semines."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir Wihuu/ kas ta Zilwe-\nka Sirđi eepreeze / ka arridsan\n(winna) Waigs no Etjes skaifts\ntohp/ un ka ta Maisė ta Zilwe-\nka Sirđi spehzina."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta KUNGA Kohki tohp\npapillam flazzinati/ tee Zeedra-\nKohki us Lithbanu/ ko wiſsch tre-\ndebsitjs."
    }
  ],
